PrecisOrder assigning the administration of public lands which are required for wildlife research, conservation or interpretation, to the Minister of the Environment, as follows: 104 hectares added to the ILES DE CONTRECOEUR National Wildlife Area ("N.W.A.") in Quebec, one hectare added to ILES DE L'ESTUAIRE N.W.A. in Quebec, and 171 hectares added to SHEPODY N.W.A. in New Brunswick.
